    "KeepAlive instructs launchd to keep the process running continuously. StartInterval schedules it to launch periodically. Combining them usually yields unpredictable behavior." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "new",
            "value" : "KeepAlive instructs launchd to keep the process running continuously. StartInterval schedules it to launch periodically. Combining them usually yields unpredictable behavior."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "KeepAlive 促使进程保持持续运行。StartInterval 用于让进程周期性启动。同时启用它们通常会导致不可预测的行为。"
          }
        }
